    <title>jailbreak command</title>
    <url>/16073915/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="连接到iphone"><a href="#连接到iphone" class="headerlink" title="连接到iphone"></a>连接到iphone</h3><ul>
<li><p>拷贝</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">通过usb端口进行映射拷贝</span><br><span class="line">scp -P 10010 ~&#x2F;Desktop&#x2F;1.txt root@localhost:~&#x2F;test</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>登录</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">初始密码 alpine</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">通过usb端口进行映射登录</span><br><span class="line">ssh root@localhost -p 10010</span><br><span class="line">ssh root@127.0.0.1 -p 10010</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>映射</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在客户端执行，这里是mac电脑</span><br><span class="line">python tcprelay.py -t 22:10010</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>密钥登录环境配置</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">先查看服务端iPhone的密钥是否配置</span><br><span class="line">路径是：~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line">如果你确定有这个文件，可以使用直接查看命令：vim ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第一步：</span><br><span class="line">在客户端生成公钥和私钥，这里是mac</span><br><span class="line">命令：ssh-keygen</span><br><span class="line">生成的公钥路径：~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">生成的私钥路径：~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;id_rsa</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第二步：</span><br><span class="line">复制客户端的公钥到服务器某路径（通过wifi拷贝）</span><br><span class="line">scp ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;id_rsa.pub root@localhost </span><br><span class="line">通过usb拷贝到服务器iPhone的</span><br><span class="line">scp -P 10010 ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;id_rsa.pub root@localhost:~</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第三步：</span><br><span class="line">追加公钥内容到授权文件尾部</span><br><span class="line">cat ~&#x2F;id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;authorized_keys</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
